<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_58729cb72965.aspx"><b>叔于田</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson58729cb72965">
叔于田，巷无居人。岂无居人？不如叔也。洵美且仁。<br />叔于狩，巷无饮酒。岂无饮酒？不如叔也。洵美且好。<br />叔适野，巷无服马。岂无服马？不如叔也。洵美且武。
